data.title: Father Unknown
data.meta_description: Father Unknown: Directed by David Quint. Captured on a camera phone as it happens, FATHER UNKNOWN is the true story of a man's struggle to face the emptiness he carries inside. Disconnected from the people closest to him and haunted by the secrecy in his family, he records his desperate search for connection on a journey with the father he's never truly known. This uplifting true story brings audiences along for the ride on a deep and powerful journey in search of connection, identity, and healing.
